name: Fire Tail Cat
description: A magical cat with a two fiery tails. Perfect companion for wizards and sorcerers.

name: Golden Dragon Ring
description: A majestic ring adorned with a two golden dragon, symbolizing power and strength.

name: Multi Winged Raven
description: A mysterious raven with multiple wings, embodying the secrets of the night. Perfect for those who appreciate enigmatic creatures.

name: Phoenix Feather Quill
description: A quill crafted from the magical feathers of a phoenix, known for enhancing creativity.

name: Sorcerer's Robe of Shadows
description: A dark robe that grants its wearer the ability to manipulate shadows. Essential for stealthy sorcerers.

name: Elixir of Eternal Youth
description: A potent elixir that bestows eternal youth upon the drinker.

name: Mystic Moon Pendant
description: A pendant featuring a mystic moon, radiating a calming aura. Ideal for those attuned to lunar energies.

name: Goblet of Infinity
description: A magical goblet with the power to endlessly refill itself. Perfect for banquets and celebrations

name: Oracle's Mirror
description: A mystical mirror that reveals glimpses of the future. Trusted by oracles and seers.

name: Slime Squid Potion
description: A peculiar potion containing essence of slime squid, known for its transformative and unpredictable effects. Use with caution!
